			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1. Enter \"spawnItem UNI_S_DebugBook_31ee023c-d151-40f6-917e-84066772783b\" into ReCon to spawn the DebugBook\r\n2. Use the DebugBook to travel to ACT1: Crash Site\r\n3. Enter \"goto -452.25, 13.51, -381.75\" into ReCon to travel into the Blighted Village smithy\r\n4. Activate the Melting Furnace\r\n5. Activate the Blacksmith's Bellows\r\n6. Enter \"create QUEST_FOR_SussurBark\" into ReCon to spawn the Sussur Tree Bark\r\n7 Enter \"create WPN_Dagger\" into ReCon to spawn a dagger in your inventory\r\n8. Use the Melting Furnace to combine the Sussur Bark with the Melting Furnace\r\n9. Exit and re-enter the Melting Furnace crafting menu\r\n10. Add the 'Dagger' to the crafting menu"
				},
